{"tid":390950,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西先知預言　世界盃前一名智利球星將死去","createTime":"2017-09-07T12:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T16:53:55.000Z","uid":4661,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9e83bae4508a1a021cc86c6dd86408d98a826943","tid":390950,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴西有一名先知卡連奴斯，最近透過電台Ovacion表示，在世界盃前一名出名的智利球員將會死去，無法參加2018世界盃，此話一出許多人揣測，這名巴西先知指的是桑契斯(Alexis Sanchez)。<br />\n<br />\n卡連奴斯先前在1年多前，曾表示會有一支足球隊遇上空難，如今查比高恩斯遭遇空難重創球隊，更令人好奇這名巴西先知的準確性。<br />\n<br />\n最近卡連奴斯再度做出死亡預測，他表示有一名智利球星將會死去，如果智利打進2018世界盃，這名智利球星不會參加，因為他即將遭遇死亡。<br />\n<br />\n2018世界盃南美洲會外賽，目前智利排在第4，不過南美洲各國差距很小，誰能晉級情勢尚未明朗化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sports.ettoday.net/news/833085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F833085&d=8IT2q3P%2Bda4EDq8PYwT7BG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f100a3c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sports.ettoday.net/news/833085</a>"},{"pid":"905c383e436d6113c29a47cc17068bb206aea785","tid":390950,"uid":35365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:01:31.000Z","msg":"得罪雲加既下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d42aecf6798d67c1ae4cbfb4ab37f92e75039eb","tid":390950,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:01:52.000Z","msg":"跟手搵人啪左佢<br />\n上位就係咁易"},{"pid":"9fb839902977248373a73e4eef5fe940abf78048","tid":390950,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:03:39.000Z","msg":"山狗斷腳死"},{"pid":"d5f698511b23d3c10da5156bbfe1926c2a473911","tid":390950,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:05:06.000Z","msg":"諗起隻八